### Image Store API - HTTP Client Requests
###
### Note: Tags are automatically normalized to lowercase for case-insensitive storage and search.
### For example, "Nature", "NATURE", and "nature" are all stored as "nature".
###
### Search results are sorted by relevance (number of matching optional tags), then by upload date (newest first).

